---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Good Enough Gaming">
  <Nav />
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1 class="page-title">About Us</h1>

      <section class="hosts-section">

        <!-- Jordan — avatar left, text right -->
        <div class="host-entry">
          <div class="host-avatar-col">
            <div class="host-avatar-circle host-avatar--pink"></div>
            <h3 class="host-name host-name--pink">Jordan</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="host-text-col">
            <p class="host-bio">I grew up with two older brothers who introduced me into gaming along with my Dad. The first system I ever played at home was the Intellivision. I have fond memories being scared as hell playing Dungeons and Dragons. As I got older I started to become more interested in RPGs, looter games and first person shooters. Right now I am lucky enough to have a PS5, Series X and a Nintendo Switch. Along with Trevor I've been an avid basketball player and we have played on the same teams since the age of 9. Go Raptors!</p>
            <div class="host-details">
              <p class="detail-label">First Game I Remember Playing</p>
              <p class="host-bio">Dungeons and Dragons on the Intellivision. Creeping through the caverns waiting for spiders and dragons to come from out of nowhere to kill me scared the hell out of me as a kid. I'll never forget the TV remote style controllers that console had.</p>
              <p class="detail-label">Top 3 Games of All Time</p>
              <ul class="top3-list top3--pink">
                <li>Megaman X</li>
                <li>Batman Arkham Series</li>
                <li>Ghost of Tsushima</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Trevor — text left, avatar right -->
        <div class="host-entry host-entry--reversed">
          <div class="host-text-col">
            <p class="host-bio">Do you relate more to a secondary character than a major one? More familiar with a Game Gear controller than a real one? Me too. As the younger (better looking) brother to Kyle, I have experienced years of Luigi-like content! From the early days of N64 Mario Kart through the Call of Duty Modern Warfare days of highschool, I'm all too familiar with getting my ass whooped in video games by my older brother.</p>
            <p class="host-bio" style="margin-top:1rem;">Currently I live off a healthy dose of PS5 adventure/RPG games with the occasional PC and Nintendo DS game thrown into the mix. Aside from the typical mainstream games I have found a lot of joy branching out into lesser played genres and indie games in recent years.</p>
            <div class="host-details">
              <p class="detail-label">Top 3 Games of All Time</p>
              <ul class="top3-list top3--teal">
                <li>The Witcher 3</li>
                <li>Skyrim</li>
                <li>Diablo</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="host-avatar-col">
            <div class="host-avatar-circle host-avatar--teal"></div>
            <h3 class="host-name host-name--teal">Trevor</h3>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Darrell — avatar left, text right -->
        <div class="host-entry">
          <div class="host-avatar-col">
            <div class="host-avatar-circle host-avatar--purple"></div>
            <h3 class="host-name host-name--purple">Darrell</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="host-text-col">
            <p class="host-bio">My sister is cooler than yours! Why, you might ask? Well that's because my sister used to work for Blockbuster, you know the old be kind and rewind place. Her working there came with many benefits such as free rentals, easy renewable rentals and a sneak peek of new systems that were coming to market. Needless to say I took full advantage and here I am a full grown adult still immersed in the world of gaming. I am very fortunate to have owned and still own every major PlayStation console, many Nintendos and even now rocking an Xbox Series X. You'll catch me playing tons of RPGs, Fighting and Racing games. My gamer tag is RedHoodHavok.</p>
            <div class="host-details">
              <p class="detail-label">First Game I Remember Playing</p>
              <p class="host-bio">The first game I ever played was Duck Hunt on NES. My next door neighbor had the system with OG Mario and Duck Hunt. I remember sneaking down in the basement there and playing all the time, when we weren't supposed to. The sound of that Nintendo gun trigger lives in my head rent free for life.</p>
              <p class="detail-label">Top 3 Games of All Time</p>
              <ul class="top3-list top3--purple">
                <li>Final Fantasy 7</li>
                <li>Injustice 2</li>
                <li>Mortal Kombat</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Kyle — text left, avatar right -->
        <div class="host-entry host-entry--reversed">
          <div class="host-text-col">
            <p class="host-bio">Growing up with Trevor, we were introduced to video games through a hand-me-down Sega Master System from our older cousin. We cut our teeth on side scrollers like WonderBoy, Altered Beast and Double Dragon, as well as Reggie Jackson Baseball and Harrier.</p>
            <p class="host-bio" style="margin-top:1rem;">Like Trevor and Jordan, I grew up playing basketball and am largely involved with sports today through my career as a teacher and basketball coach. I largely find myself playing FPS games, as well as looter RPG type games, with a smattering of extreme sports games sprinkled into the mix.</p>
            <div class="host-details">
              <p class="detail-label">Top 3 Games of All Time</p>
              <ul class="top3-list top3--cyan">
                <li>Call of Duty: MW2 (2009)</li>
                <li>Diablo 3</li>
                <li>World of Warcraft</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="host-avatar-col">
            <div class="host-avatar-circle host-avatar--cyan"></div>
            <h3 class="host-name host-name--cyan">Kyle</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="listen-section">
        <h2 class="section-heading section-heading--listen">Listen &amp; Follow</h2>
        <div class="listen-links">
          <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/3x1nEjDu2Y0ce19FGTXPyo" class="listen-link listen-link--spotify" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Spotify</a>
          <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/ca/podcast/good-enough-gaming-pod/id1553128355" class="listen-link listen-link--apple" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Podcasts</a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@GoodEnoughGamingPod" class="listen-link listen-link--youtube" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</Layout>

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,300&display=swap');

  body { min-height: 100vh; background: #13151a; }

  main {
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    max-width: 72rem;
    color: white;
    margin-top: 8rem;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #4ddbff;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-shadow:
      1px 1px 0 #003344, 2px 2px 0 #002a38, 3px 3px 0 #001a24,
      4px 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),
      0 0 20px #4ddbff, 0 0 50px #4ddbff, 0 0 90px #df53f5;
  }

  /* Intro */
  .intro-section {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .intro-text {
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #cac7ff;
    text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(167,164,224,0.4);
  }

  /* Section headings */
  .section-heading {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #00d4aa;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-shadow:
      1px 1px 0 #003328, 2px 2px 0 #002820, 3px 3px 0 #001d18,
      4px 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),
      0 0 20px #00d4aa, 0 0 50px #00ffcc;
  }
  .section-heading--listen {
    color: #ff8c00;
    text-shadow:
      1px 1px 0 #7a3800, 2px 2px 0 #5a2400, 3px 3px 0 #3a1400,
      4px 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7),
      0 0 20px #ff8c00, 0 0 50px #ff6500;
  }

  /* Host entries — staggered layout */
  .hosts-section { margin-bottom: 5rem; }

  .host-entry {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0d0d1a 0%, #12101f 100%);
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .host-avatar-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .host-avatar-circle {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .host-name {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .host-text-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }

  .host-bio {
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #c8c4ff;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .host-details { margin-top: 1.5rem; }

  .detail-label {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #a7a4e0;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 0.6rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .top3-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  .top3-list li {
    font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .top3-list li::before {
    content: '▶';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    top: 0.3rem;
  }

  /* Avatar colors */
  .host-avatar--pink   { border: 2px solid #ff6ec7; box-shadow: 0 0 14px #ff6ec7, 0 0 35px rgba(255,110,199,0.25); }
  .host-avatar--teal   { border: 2px solid #00d4aa; box-shadow: 0 0 14px #00d4aa, 0 0 35px rgba(0,212,170,0.25); }
  .host-avatar--purple { border: 2px solid #a855f7; box-shadow: 0 0 14px #a855f7, 0 0 35px rgba(168,85,247,0.25); }
  .host-avatar--cyan   { border: 2px solid #4ddbff; box-shadow: 0 0 14px #4ddbff, 0 0 35px rgba(77,219,255,0.25); }

  /* Name colors */
  .host-name--pink   { color: #ff6ec7; text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff6ec7; }
  .host-name--teal   { color: #00d4aa; text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00d4aa; }
  .host-name--purple { color: #c084fc; text-shadow: 0 0 10px #a855f7; }
  .host-name--cyan   { color: #4ddbff; text-shadow: 0 0 10px #4ddbff; }

  /* Top 3 bullet colors */
  .top3--pink   li { color: #ff6ec7; } .top3--pink   li::before { color: #ff6ec7; }
  .top3--teal   li { color: #00d4aa; } .top3--teal   li::before { color: #00d4aa; }
  .top3--purple li { color: #c084fc; } .top3--purple li::before { color: #a855f7; }
  .top3--cyan   li { color: #4ddbff; } .top3--cyan   li::before { color: #4ddbff; }

  /* Card border per host */
  .host-entry:nth-child(1) { border: 1px solid rgba(255,110,199,0.3); box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,110,199,0.07); }
  .host-entry:nth-child(2) { border: 1px solid rgba(0,212,170,0.3);   box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0,212,170,0.07); }
  .host-entry:nth-child(3) { border: 1px solid rgba(168,85,247,0.3);  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(168,85,247,0.07); }
  .host-entry:nth-child(4) { border: 1px solid rgba(77,219,255,0.3);  box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(77,219,255,0.07); }

  /* Listen links */
  .listen-section { margin-bottom: 5rem; text-align: center; }
  .listen-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .listen-link {
    font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .listen-link:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .listen-link--spotify { color: #13151a; background: #1db954; box-shadow: 0 0 12px #1db954, 0 0 30px rgba(29,185,84,0.3); }
  .listen-link--spotify:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 20px #1db954, 0 0 50px rgba(29,185,84,0.5); }
  .listen-link--apple   { color: #13151a; background: #ff6ec7; box-shadow: 0 0 12px #ff6ec7, 0 0 30px rgba(255,110,199,0.3); }
  .listen-link--apple:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff6ec7, 0 0 50px rgba(255,110,199,0.5); }
  .listen-link--youtube { color: #13151a; background: #ff4444; box-shadow: 0 0 12px #ff4444, 0 0 30px rgba(255,68,68,0.3); }
  .listen-link--youtube:hover { box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff4444, 0 0 50px rgba(255,68,68,0.5); }

  /* Desktop — staggered side-by-side */
  @media (min-width: 64rem) {
    main { margin-top: 10rem; }
    .page-title { font-size: 2.5rem; }

    .host-entry {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 3rem;
      padding: 3rem;
    }
    .host-entry--reversed {
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }
    .host-avatar-col { min-width: 160px; }
    .host-avatar-circle { width: 150px; height: 150px; }
  }
</style>
